yaml
=====

use yaml for better configuration.
documentation can be seen at: http://pyyaml.org/wiki/PyYAMLDocumentation
full specification: http://yaml.org/spec/1.1/
and a simple wikipedia version: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YAML
and the best: http://learnxinyminutes.com/docs/yaml/

    sudo apt-get install python-yaml

some caveats:
  http://stackoverflow.com/questions/5484016/how-can-i-do-string-concatenation-or-string-replacement-in-yaml


py.test
========

sudo apt-get install python-pytest
